{"tid":530770,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日午餐 僞宮保雞丁","createTime":"2018-01-16T06:24:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T12:10:36.000Z","uid":43041,"like":10,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bb12b8f0f7c1f38b9da324a36af95383585145c4","tid":530770,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:24:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/141246_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F141246_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=aa698021&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n切薑片 切蔥 切雞肉<br />\n豉油粟粉砂糖醃雞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/141459_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F141459_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9ac4513c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n落油炒腰果至轉色，放埋一邊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/141544_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F141544_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=af3d6182&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n爆香薑片兩塊，落辣椒油炒雞肉，再放埋一邊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/141713_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F141713_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9ca3e845&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n爆香蔥薑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/141731_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F141731_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0effc0db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n倒曬d雞同腰果入去炒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/141825_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F141825_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e27c7188&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n倒埋個李錦記宮保雞丁醬入去炒多陣就上碟<br />\n<br />\n屌拿星個醬陣花椒味會唔會重得濟啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食完成個口得花椒味其他咩味都食唔出"},{"pid":"29bc82763e4b19b55b903d93646fe9481f7ca224","tid":530770,"uid":5522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:42:38.000Z","msg":"雞肉再煎香少少 會唔會比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7bceafb2825f9540b759d683694efc6dbf55be8","tid":530770,"uid":56240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:43:33.000Z","msg":"食屎"},{"pid":"1d9054d507c2bb4c110f685f62f1b8dcc90437e2","tid":530770,"uid":42734,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:46:12.000Z","msg":"巴打好勁識煮咁多野"},{"pid":"8c38c7ad1e37407b969a6045e9cb1400950011e4","tid":530770,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29bc82763e4b19b55b903d93646fe9481f7ca224","tid":530770,"uid":5522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:42:38.000Z","msg":"雞肉再煎香少少 會唔會比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:51:08.000Z","msg":"今次比上次煎耐左，下次再煎耐d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c009b31a5f23fe6b201e47715ab575fee53ea79","tid":530770,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7bceafb2825f9540b759d683694efc6dbf55be8","tid":530770,"uid":56240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:43:33.000Z","msg":"食屎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今次煮得唔好食"},{"pid":"fc9159a95c664c84d14101d63fa09d1bdba57d7f","tid":530770,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor